notes.note:
Email sent for required documents: 

Good afternoon Rupinder, 
I'm writing to let you know that I have taken over the handling of your claim. I reviewed all of the documents that you have submitted and it appears as though there are still some missing documents that we need in order to process your claim: 
- Automobile Insurance Policy - We need the full policy sent to you by your insurance company. If you do not have this document, your broker/insurance company should be able to help you obtain it. - Details of any arrears including penalties on the financial loan - The easiest document to obtain for this is a transaction summary of all payments made on your automobile loan to the bank. I would recommend calling your bank and asking them to email you this document. 
Please let me know if you have any questions or concerns. 
Thank you, 
Sarah Gabor
